data.description: When it comes to finding the perfect home to plant your roots, you will hit a bullseye with this one! This adorable cbs home is situated on a large lot with a privacy fence around the backyard. Metal Roof, Brand new impact windows just installed, Laminate wood floors, crown molding, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, covered patio and plenty of space to parking a boat or RV. This home and location has so much to offer and is ready for its next owners, act now before it's too late.
